

1. Empty World:

$ roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_empty_world.launch


2. *** TurtleBot3 World (Most Important) ****:

$ roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_world.launch

In a new terminal, type the following command to move the TB3 manually:

$ roslaunch turtlebot3_teleop turtlebot3_teleop_key.launch

Use the keyboard (i.e. w,s,x,a,d) to move the robot around

In a new terminal, type the following command to monitor topics via rqt

$ rqt


3. House World:

$ roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_house.launch
